_pRange.descriptionZh: 发起作用（或产生某种结果）的人或物
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The direct performer or driver of the action (animate or inanimate). e.g. John wrote a book.

_pRange.descriptionZh: 出席某一活动的组织或个人。

_pRange.descriptionZh: 出席某一活动的组织或个人。 (拼写单数形式，attendee)。

_pRange.descriptionZh: 与该产品或服务相关的品牌，或者是由该组织或个人维护的品牌。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The brand(s) associated with a product or service, or the brand(s) maintained by an organization or business person.
_pRange.rdfs:label: brand

_pRange.descriptionZh: 广播网络的内容来自的站点
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The media network(s) whose content is broadcast on this station.
_pRange.rdfs:label: broadcastAffiliateOf

_pRange.descriptionZh: 拥有或经营广播服务的组织。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The organization owning or operating the broadcast service.
_pRange.rdfs:label: broadcaster

_pRange.descriptionZh: 安排买方和卖方进行交易的实体。 大多数情况下，经纪人从未获取或发布交易所涉及的产品或服务的所有权。

In most cases a broker never acquires or releases ownership of a product or service involved in an exchange.  If it is not clear whether an entity is a broker, seller, or buyer, the latter two terms are preferred.
_pRange.rdfs:label: broker

_pRange.rdfs:label: carrier

_pRange.rdfs:comment: A sub property of recipient. The recipient copied on a message.
_pRange.rdfs:label: ccRecipient

_pRange.descriptionZh: 写了一首作曲的人或者组织，或者是在一些活动上表演的一部作品的作曲家。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The person or organization who wrote a composition, or who is the composer of a work performed at some event.
_pRange.rdfs:label: composer

_pRange.descriptionZh: CreativeWork协助者/次级贡献者。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A secondary contributor to the CreativeWork or Event.
_pRange.rdfs:label: contributor

_pRange.descriptionZh: CreativeWork合法版权的拥有者。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The party holding the legal copyright to the CreativeWork.
_pRange.rdfs:label: copyrightHolder

_pRange.descriptionZh: 该 CreativeWork 的创作者/作者。跟CreativeWork的Author属性一样。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The creator/author of this CreativeWork. This is the same as the Author property for CreativeWork.
_pRange.rdfs:label: creator

_pRange.descriptionZh: 一个作品除主要作者外的其他贡献者，例如 “Red and Blue”那首歌的贡献者是“Stefani Germanotta乐队”，但是主唱是Lady Gaga。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The group the release is credited to if different than the byArtist. For example, Red and Blue is credited to "Stefani Germanotta Band", but by Lady Gaga.
_pRange.rdfs:label: creditedTo

_pRange.descriptionZh: 下单或支付单据的一方。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: Party placing the order or paying the invoice.
_pRange.rdfs:label: customer

_pRange.descriptionZh: 组织与该组织某个部门之间的关系，也被描述成组织（允许不同的网址，标识，开放时间）。 例如：一家有药店的商店，或者是一间带咖啡厅的面包店。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A relationship between an organization and a department of that organization, also described as an organization (allowing different urls, logos, opening hours). For example: a store with a pharmacy, or a bakery with a cafe.
_pRange.rdfs:label: department

_pRange.descriptionZh: 参与者的子属性。 被支持的人/组织。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A sub property of participant. The person/organization being supported.
_pRange.rdfs:label: endorsee

_pRange.descriptionZh: 社交网络上被别人关注
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A sub property of object. The person or organization being followed.
_pRange.rdfs:label: followee

_pRange.descriptionZh: 通过某种财务贡献支持（赞助）某事的个人或组织。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A person or organization that supports (sponsors) something through some kind of financial contribution.
_pRange.rdfs:label: funder

_pRange.descriptionZh: 获得此许可的人员，组织，联络人或受众。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The person, organization, contact point, or audience that has been granted this permission.
_pRange.rdfs:label: grantee

_pRange.descriptionZh: 提供工作职位的机构
_pRange.rdfs:comment: Organization offering the job position.
_pRange.rdfs:label: hiringOrganization

_pRange.descriptionZh: 航空公司，旅游俱乐部等提供会员资格的组织
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The organization (airline, travelers' club, etc.) the membership is made with.
_pRange.rdfs:label: hostingOrganization

_pRange.descriptionZh: 许可的签发机构
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The organization issuing the ticket or permit.
_pRange.rdfs:label: issuedBy

_pRange.descriptionZh: 房地产业主
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A sub property of participant. The owner of the real estate property.
_pRange.rdfs:label: landlord

_pRange.descriptionZh: 借出东西给别人的人
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A sub property of participant. The person that lends the object being borrowed.
_pRange.rdfs:label: lender

_pRange.descriptionZh: 产品的制造商
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The manufacturer of the product.
_pRange.rdfs:label: manufacturer

_pRange.descriptionZh: 组织或项目的成员
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A member of an Organization or a ProgramMembership. Organizations can be members of organizations; ProgramMembership is typically for individuals.
_pRange.rdfs:label: member

_pRange.descriptionZh: 会员所属的机构或项目组织
_pRange.rdfs:comment: An Organization (or ProgramMembership) to which this Person or Organization belongs.
_pRange.rdfs:label: memberOf

_pRange.descriptionZh: 组织的会员
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A member of this organization.
_pRange.rdfs:label: members

_pRange.descriptionZh: 属性'seller'的旧称（这样的陈旧条目是否应该删掉）
_pRange.rdfs:comment: 'merchant' is an out-dated term for 'seller'.
_pRange.rdfs:label: merchant

_pRange.descriptionZh: 活动的组织者
_pRange.rdfs:comment: An organizer of an Event.
_pRange.rdfs:label: organizer

_pRange.descriptionZh: subOrganization的反向属性，即包含这个组织的更大组织

_pRange.descriptionZh: 活动中的表演者，例如主持人，音乐家，音乐团体或演员
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A performer at the event—for example, a presenter, musician, musical group or actor.
_pRange.rdfs:label: performer

_pRange.descriptionZh: 主要表演者或表演者，例如主持人，音乐家或演员
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The main performer or performers of the event—for example, a presenter, musician, or actor.
_pRange.rdfs:label: performers

_pRange.descriptionZh: 制作作品（例如音乐，电影，电视剧等）的人或者组织

_pRange.rdfs:label: producer

_pRange.descriptionZh: 项目（例如电视剧，视频，游戏，剧集）的生产公司或者工作室
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The production company or studio responsible for the item e.g. series, video game, episode etc.
_pRange.rdfs:label: productionCompany

_pRange.descriptionZh: 服务提供商，服务运营商或服务执行者; 货物生产者。 另一方（卖方）可以代表提供者提供这些服务或商品。 提供商也可以作为卖方。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The service provider, service operator, or service performer; the goods producer. Another party (a seller) may offer those services or goods on behalf of the provider. A provider may also serve as the seller.
_pRange.rdfs:label: provider

_pRange.descriptionZh: 作品的出版商
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The publisher of the creative work.
_pRange.rdfs:label: publisher

_pRange.descriptionZh: 参与者的子属性。 在行动接收端的参与者。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A sub property of participant. The participant who is at the receiving end of the action.
_pRange.rdfs:label: recipient

_pRange.descriptionZh: 音乐作品的发布厂商，即通常所说的唱片公司，例如德唱，迪卡（decca)。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The label that issued the release.
_pRange.rdfs:label: recordLabel

_pRange.descriptionZh: 评论网页内容（准确性、完整性）的人或者组织
_pRange.rdfs:comment: People or organizations that have reviewed the content on this web page for accuracy and/or completeness.
_pRange.rdfs:label: reviewedBy

_pRange.descriptionZh: 提供商品出售、物品租赁、贷款等服务的人或组织。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: An entity which offers (sells / leases / lends / loans) the services / goods.  A seller may also be a provider.
_pRange.rdfs:label: seller

_pRange.descriptionZh: 参与者的子属性。例如邮件的发送者。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A sub property of participant. The participant who is at the sending end of the action.
_pRange.rdfs:label: sender

_pRange.descriptionZh: 不同于提供商（provider）提供服务，运营商（例如分包商）运营服务
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The operating organization, if different from the provider.  This enables the representation of services that are provided by an organization, but operated by another organization like a subcontractor.
_pRange.rdfs:label: serviceOperator

_pRange.descriptionZh: 创作者代表哪个机构工作的
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The Organization on whose behalf the creator was working.
_pRange.rdfs:label: sourceOrganization

_pRange.descriptionZh: 通过质押，承诺或财政捐助支持事物的人或组织。 例如 医学研究的赞助者或事件的公司赞助商。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A person or organization that supports a thing through a pledge, promise, or financial contribution. e.g. a sponsor of a Medical Study or a corporate sponsor of an event.
_pRange.rdfs:label: sponsor

_pRange.descriptionZh: 两个组织之间的关系。其中第二个组织，例如以子公司的名字，属于第一个组织。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A relationship between two organizations where the first includes the second, e.g., as a subsidiary. See also: the more specific 'department' property.
_pRange.rdfs:label: subOrganization

_properties.descriptionZh: 描述作品主要创作方的编辑原则的页面链接
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The publishingPrinciples property indicates (typically via URL) a document describing the editorial principles of an Organization (or individual e.g. a Person writing a blog) that relate to their activities as a publisher, e.g. ethics or diversity policies. When applied to a CreativeWork (e.g. NewsArticle) the principles are those of the party primarily responsible for the creation of the CreativeWork.

While such policies are most typically expressed in natural language, sometimes related information (e.g. indicating a funder) can be expressed using cnschema.org terminology.
_properties.rdfs:label: publishingPrinciples

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的一个附加类型， 通常用于从外部词典中向微数据语法添加更加具体的类型。它表示事物和事物本身所属的类之间的关系。在RDFa语法中, 对多类型最好使用‘typeof’属性这样的本地RDFa语法. Schema.org 工具对额外类型的理解较弱，特别是外部定义的额外类型。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An additional type for the item, typically used for adding more specific types from external vocabularies in microdata syntax. This is a relationship between something and a class that the thing is in. In RDFa syntax, it is better to use the native RDFa syntax - the 'typeof' attribute - for multiple types. Schema.org tools may have only weaker understanding of extra types, in particular those defined externally.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalType
